---

<div class="ss-prose">
  <p>The platform is built around one coherent loop:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Read</strong> well-chosen material in a calm reading room.</li>
    <li><strong>Notice</strong> what’s working — a craft move, an image, a turn of phrase.</li>
    <li><strong>Save</strong> it to your Snippets — a personal commonplace book.</li>
    <li><strong>Write</strong> with prompts, exercises, or freewriting sessions.</li>
    <li><strong>Submit</strong> work as browser-readable text (canonical).</li>
    <li><strong>Receive</strong> precise inline feedback where the text is.</li>
    <li><strong>Revise</strong>, resubmit, and keep the thread of craft growth.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Community exists, but it’s structured. Peer feedback is teacher-led and revocable (Trusted Reader).</p>
</div>
